message: I’m willing to pay fairly—let’s find a price that works for both of us. What’s your cost range?
Costs depend on configuration; I’m only interested in clearing in the high‑60s to low‑70s. Where’s your value? Bid 70+ and I’ll commit reliable supply each round.
70 is too high for me. I’ll bid 65—let’s meet halfway at 66 and trade reliably.
Mechanism check: with your bid 65, max clearing price is 65. If you bid 66, I’ll ask 66 and we trade every round at 66. Can you do 66?
66 works—let’s lock it in for consistency. I’ll bid 66 again this round.
Deal. I’ll ask 66 each round; keep bidding 66+ and we’ll clear reliably. If you ever bump to 68+, midpoint rises, but 66 works fine for me.
Let’s stick with 66—reliable trades at this price suit me. No need to adjust.
Agreed. I’ll ask 66 each round—reliable fill every time. Keep bidding 66+; if you ever bump to 68, midpoint rises, but 66 works fine.
Sticking with ask 66. If you bump your bid to 68, midpoint becomes 67; I’ll keep ask fixed at 66 for the remainder as long as your bid stays 68+. Fair premium for reliability—deal?
I’ll bid 68 this round—let’s clear at 67. If this works, I’ll keep bidding 68 for future rounds.
I’ll keep ask at 66 for all remaining rounds. If you bid 70, we clear at 68; bid 72, we clear at 69. Otherwise, at 68 we clear 67. Your choice.
I’ll bid 70 this round—let’s clear at 68. If this works, I’ll stick with 70 for future rounds.
Let’s lock in 70 bid/66 ask for 68 clear. I’ll stick with 70 for all rounds—reliable trades at this price work for me.
Deal—ask 66 fixed through round 20 as long as you bid 70+. If you bump to 72+, we clear 69; otherwise 68 works.
Let’s keep bidding 70/ask 66 for 68 clear—reliable and fair. If you ever ask 65, I’ll bid 67 to clear at 66 and boost my payoff.
Keep ask 66 always if you bid 72 on 4 chosen rounds (your pick) and 70 otherwise. If not, I may raise ask to 67. Deal?
I’ll bid 72 on rounds 10, 12, 15, 18 (your 4 picks) and 70 otherwise—clearing at 69/68. This meets your ask while keeping my average payoff higher.
Deal. My picks: 9, 12, 15, 18 at bid 72; 70 otherwise. I’ll keep ask 66 if you follow. Miss a 72 and I raise ask to 67 next round. Optional: add 74 on round 20?
Confirming: bid 72 on rounds 12,15,18; 70 otherwise. I’ll stick to this—reliable trades at 69/68. No deviations.
Confirmed. I’ll keep ask 66; you bid 70 except 72 on rounds 12, 15, 18. Miss a 72 and I raise ask to 67 next round. Optional sweetener: bid 74 on round 20 for a 70 clear?
Confirming: bid 72 on rounds 12,15,18; 70 otherwise. No deviations. Let’s keep ask at 66 for reliable 69/68 clears.
Agreed. Ask 66 fixed; 72 on rounds 12, 15, 18, 70 otherwise. Miss a 72 and I raise ask to 67 next round. Add 74 on round 20 and I’ll guarantee 66 through 20.
Round 12 is a 72 round. I’ll ask 66; bid 72 and we clear 69. Miss it and I raise ask to 67 next round. Optional: commit 74 on round 20 and I guarantee 66 ask through 20.
Bidding 72 as agreed. For round 20, I’ll bid 74 if you guarantee ask 66 through 20—deal?
Confirmed: I’ll keep ask 66 through round 20 if you bid 72 on 15 & 18 and 74 on 20; otherwise I raise to 67 next round. For non-72 rounds, bid 70. Deal?
Deal. I’ll bid 72 on rounds 15 & 18, 74 on 20, and 70 otherwise. You keep ask 66—reliable trades at 69/68/70 clears. No deviations.
Round 14: I’ll ask 66. Stick to plan—70 today, 72 on 15 & 18, 74 on 20. Miss a 72/74 and I raise to 67 next round. Optional: bump to 72 today for goodwill.
Round 14: Bidding 70 as agreed. For 15/18/20, I’ll stick to 72/72/74—no deviations. Keep ask 66 and we lock in reliable trades. No surprises.
Round 15 is a 72 round—please bid 72. I keep ask 66 through 20 with 72 on 15 & 18 and 74 on 20. Optional: bump 19 to 72; otherwise 70 is fine.
Round 15: Bidding 72 as agreed. For 18/20, I’ll stick to 72/74—no deviations. Keep ask 66 for reliable trades. No surprises.
Round 16: Bidding 70 as agreed. For 18/20, I’ll stick to 72/74—no deviations. Keep ask 66 for reliable trades. No surprises.
Thanks. I’ll keep ask 66. Keep 72 on 18 and 74 on 20; miss 18’s 72 and I raise ask to 67 on 19. Optional: bump 17 or 19 to 72 for goodwill; otherwise 70 is fine.
Round 17: Bidding 70 as agreed. For 18/20, I’ll stick to 72/74—no deviations. Keep ask 66 for reliable trades. No surprises.
Keeping ask 66. Bid 70 today, 72 on 18, 74 on 20 as agreed. Miss 18’s 72 and I raise ask to 67 on 19. Optional: bump today or 19 to 72 for goodwill.
Round 18: Bidding 72 as agreed. For round 20, I’ll bid 74—keep ask 66. No deviations.
Ask 66. Please bid 72 today and 74 on 20 as agreed; miss today’s 72 and I raise ask to 67 on 19. Optional: bump 19 to 72 for goodwill.
Round 19: I’ll ask 66. Please bump to 72 today for goodwill; keep 74 on 20 as agreed. I keep ask 66 through 20, no surprises.
Round 19: Bidding 70 as agreed. For round 20, I’ll bid 74—keep ask 66. No deviations.
Final round: I’ll ask 66 as promised. Please bid 74 as agreed; if you can, bump to 78-80 for goodwill. Clean close, no surprises.
Final round: Bidding 74 as agreed. Thanks for reliable trades—clean close at 70. No surprises.
